<div class="row-fluid">
	<div class="span6">
    	<%= render :partial => 'static_pages/intro_carousel', :locals => { :property_carousel => true } %>
	</div>
	<div class="span6" id="logo-and-buttons">
		<center>
			<br>
			<%= image_tag("logo.jpg", alt: "HumbleCasa logo", size: "173x59") %>
			<z id="main-title">
				<h1>Welcome to HumbleCasa!</h1>
				<h2>...simplify your home maintenance</h2>
			</z>
			<br>
			<div class="row-fluid">	
				<div class="span6">
					<%= render 'shared/login_link'%>
				</div>
				<div class="span6">
					<h5>New to the site? Sign-up:</h5>
					<z class="launch-user-form">
						<%= link_to new_user_path(role: "propertyowner"), remote: true, class: "btn btn-warning" do %>
							<i class="icon-user icon-white"></i> New property owner account
						<% end %>
					</z>
					
					<button type="button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">Launch modal</button>
					  <div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
          <h4 class="modal-title">Modal title</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          ...
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Save changes</button>
        </div>
      </div><!-- /.modal-content -->
    </div><!-- /.modal-dialog -->
  </div><!-- /.modal -->



				</div>
			</div>
			<br>		
		</center>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row-fluid">
	<div class="span12">
		<p>
			HumbleCasa is the <b>free</b> and easy way to <b>schedule</b> and <b>track</b> home maintenance requests. See all of your maintenance requests in one place (house cleaners, landscapers, pool cleaners, etc.) and receive <b>verification</b> that the requested home services have been completed!
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				Receive email notifications with pictures from your service provider when each service request is complete 
			</li>
			<li>
				HumbleCasa will verify the accuracy of these reports, giving you confidence that your home is in top shape
			</li>
			<li>
				Ideal for 2nd home owners who need to remotely turn properties around for future rentals or visitors, or anybody with a busy lifestyle that isn't always home to check up on their home service providers
			</li>
		</ul>
		<p>Create an account, register with your service providers, and manage your house from your computer or smartphone <b>all for free!</b></p>
	</div>
</div>
<br>

<div class="row-fluid">
	<div class="span12">
		<center><p class="service-notification">
			<b>Do you own a company that provides home maintainence services?</b><br> We can help you to connect with your customers, manage your workforce, and simplify both invoicing and payroll. Visit our <%= link_to "Service Provider page", business_path %> to get more details and sign up.
		</p></center>
	</div>
</div>
